    "Moreover, a new skillset in healthcare providers and technical assistants is also needed to ensure processes are running efficiently.",
    "In the future, substantial investments are required to make healthcare infrastructure ready for a routine deployment of DLbased biomarkers (Fig. 2b).Finally, for DL to be adopted by practitioners, the models should ideally not be considered as a \"black box\", but also inherit the explainability for their decisions (Fig.",
